text:
<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates>
We are investigating increased error rates for some Application Load Balancers in the US-EAST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates>
Between 1:53 PM and 2:29 PM PST, we experienced connectivity issues for Web Application Firewall enabled Application Load Balancers in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
